        <dt>Printer</dt> <!-- Term -->
        <dd>Printer is an output device which provides a hard copy of the output.</dd> <!-- Definition -->
        <dt>Monitor</dt> <!-- Term -->
        <dd>Monitor is an output device which provides a soft copy of the output.</dd> <!-- Definition -->
